## WorkerTilerProtocol.TileRequest interface

This object is sent to the tiler asking to retrieve a specific tile. The expected response type is an object containing a tiled payload.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
interface TileRequest extends WorkerServiceProtocol.ServiceRequest
```
